import React from 'react'
import { SidebarContainer, Icon, CloseIcon } from './SidebarElement';

const Sidebar = () => {
  return (
    <SidebarContainer>
        <Icon>
            <CloseIcon />
        </Icon>
        <SidebarWrapper>
          <SidebarLink to="about">
            Sobre
          </SidebarLink>
          <SidebarLink to="discover">
            Discover
          </SidebarLink>
          <SidebarLink to="services">
            Services
          </SidebarLink>
          <SidebarLink to="signup">
            Sign Up
          </SidebarLink>
        </SidebarWrapper>
    </SidebarContainer>
  )
}

export default Sidebar
